OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A father whose 12-year-old son was     
OL,6, killed by an IRA bomb 30 years ago has 
OL,7, said campaigning for peace is "the glue
OL,8, which has kept the family together".   
OL,10,FTim Parry and three-year-old Johnathan 
OL,11,FBall died and 54 others were hurt when 
OL,12,Ftwo bombs hidden inside litter bins    
OL,13,Fexploded on 20 March 1993.             
OL,15,FThe Provisional IRA acknowledged its   
OL,16,Finvolvement the following day.         
OL,18,FColin Parry said he and his wife Wendy 
OL,19,Fhad "focussed so much on turning       
OL,20,Fsomething bad into something good".    
